(3652, '', '2024-12-20', 'Hon. Zohria S. Bansil- Guro  - Mayor', 'MDN - We are submitting herewith request for realignment of Hon. Zohria S. Bansil- Guro of Matanog Municipality of the project 24-RIMNRD321: Reconstruction of Road at Sitio Campo I, Brgy. Sapad, Matanog funded under Regular Infrastructure Projects FY 2024 and to be implemented \"By Contract\". The necessity for realignment has arisen as the current alignment overlaps with a project that is being funded by the Provincial Government of Maguindanao del Norte. As a result, it has become essential to establish a new alignment to avoid conflicts and ensure the successful implementation of both projects. Accordingly, the proposed new location is located nearby the original location., Matanog, ,', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1994oxHmgLvbu30eNCXJhIho4O5MICqBS/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Prepare MEMO to DEO', ''),
(3653, '', '2024-12-20', 'ATTY. PAISALIN P. TAGO -  Deputy Speaker Bangsamoro Parliament', 'LDS1 - I am writing to request a comprehensive list of all projects undertaken by the Ministry of Public Works (MPW) in the province of Lanao del Sur from 2020 to the present. The requested list should include details such as the project name, location, allocated budget, and any other relevant information.\nThis information is crucial to our ongoing review and planning efforts, as we seek to better contribute to the development and progress of the Bangsamoro Region.\nShould there be any questions or clarifications, please do not hesitate to reach our office at 0921-858-3510 or via email at mptago@gmail.com.\nWe look forward to your prompt and favorable response to this request., LDS, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1izRIelItQO7oSG2ug2b6UbFoezg9dFpo/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Prepare the list and response letter', ''),
