(3662, '', '2024-12-26', 'RANDY R. BEL ROSARIO, CESO III Director V  - Stakeholders Relations Service', 'SUL1 - May we respectfully endorse the letter from Sultan Sharif Jubair Bin Sultan Sharif Mohammad Pulalun Amirul-Mu\'minin, Chairman of the United Tausug Citizens, received through Citizens\' Feedback Management Center, requesting for assistance in the construction of various housing and infrastructure projects for the Province of Sulu with details attached.\n\n, Sulu, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/19x9V1zjwSkBBm1RktS3ddmCnB2IUL_gl/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- endorse to OCM', ''),
(3663, '', '2024-12-26', 'Monera O. Abdul  - Punong Baranggay', 'MDN - Resolution Requesting Water System at Sittio km17 Baranggay Ladia, Sultan Kudarat Maguindanao Del Norte;\nWhereas, for serious consideration of the August body is a felt need to install Water System at Sittio km17 Baranggay Ladia, Sultan Kudarat Maguindanao Del Norte;\nWhere for upon unanimous approval of the august body is a felt need to install Water System at Sittio km17 Baranggay Ladia Sultan Kudarat Mag. Del Norte where fore for upon unanimous approval of the august body it\nwas;\nResolved as it is hereby resolved to adopt a resolution requesting the honorable Regional Office Engr. Danilo A. Ong O.I.C Ministry to fund the installation of said one (1) unit of Water System at Sittio km17 Baranggay Ladia Sultan Kudarat Maguindanao Del Norte;\nPrepared By: Solaiman S. Saban\nCooperative Chairman\n, Sultan Kudarat, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1nBNZ_DZUIe-EQ2gohnI2aBHQlsQq2O0I/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Consider of FF.', ''),
(3664, '', '2024-12-26', 'HON. ABDULHAMID M. ABAS  - Punong Barangay', 'MDN - We would like to request for street lights to light up the interior and exterior areas of Barangay Makir. Our Barangay is among the heavily populated Barangay of Datu Odin Sinsuat, Maguindanao Del Norte, with interior Barangay roads interconnecting one another.\nThe provisions of said facility will improve social dynamics of residents and could facilitate activities even during night time. Furthermore, this could also prevent proliferations of unnecessary activities which usually happens during night time such as motor abduction, insurgencies, bullying activities and others. Thus it will lead to the promotion of stable peace and order inside the Barangay premises.\n\n\n, Datu Odin Sinsuat, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UcS-kKrFD0eQMMszfWv2UuV9DLrM6zpr/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- endorse to deo', ''),
(3665, '', '2024-12-26', 'SF04 Anthony H Paculdo  - City Fire Marshal  Lamitan City Fire Station', 'BAS - Hope this finds you well. This letter is to formally request from your good office the Concreting of Pavements and Garage Flooring of Lamitan City Fire Station, where it accommodates 5 fire trucks and 1 ambulance such is imperative to enhance station\'s functionality and ensure the efficient and safe deployment of emergency vehicles.\nPresently, the existing pavement and garage flooring are composed of earth soil with stones and gravel paths rendering navigation difficult and hazardous especially in adverse weather conditions. The surfaces become muddy when wet and dusty when dry, posing challenges such as potential vehicle damage. By concreting these, we can establish a smooth and resilient surface that will bolster our fire preparedness and facilitate a prompt and effective response to emergencies.,  Lamitan City, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/17pAlZmcG8OFeSnFmAn4JXekCDvyeqjUK/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- endorse to milg', ''),
(3666, '', '2024-12-26', 'HON. JOHARTO U. BINANGON  - Barangay Chairmah 0965-889-0547', 'COT - 1.Construction of Various Road, Barangay Rosary Heights XI, Cotabato City.- Barangay Rosary  Heights XI, Cotabato City.2.5 km\n2.Construction of CHILD FRIENDLY PARK - Federville Subdivision, Barangay Rosary Heights XI, Cotabato City 150-300 square meters\n3. Construction  and Improvements of Various Drainage Canal City - Barangay Rosary Heights XI,RH  Cotabato City 2.3 km,  Cotabato City, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Y4FawCINMjMa3RK4dKdLbpvWqZPpiU3F/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- consider for FF.', ''),
(3667, '', '2024-12-26', 'MODRIKA M. ABDULLAH - Secretary', 'MDS - Respectfully transmitting to DANILO A. ONG, Officer-in-Charge, Ministry of Public Works (MPW)-BARMM, the herein endorsement from ALVIN-YASHER K ABDULGAFAR, Chief of Staff, Office of the Chief Minister (OCM)-BARMM, forwarding the letter from MODRIKA M. ABDULLAH, Secretary, United Familica of Bangga Makalangas (UFBM), Inc., requesting the construction of small bridge across Sitio Bangga creek in Barangay Old Maganoy, Datu Abdullah Sangki, Maguindanao del Sur., Datu Abdullah Sangki, ,', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1m7gEn76sLzSLk9E8Qi9LDAhzaAp8ARPv/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- consider for FF.', ''),
(3668, '', '2024-12-26', 'HON. ADRULFA PASAWIRAN  - Barangay Chairman', 'MDN - Respectfully forwarded to DANILO A. ONG, Bangsamoro Director General, Officer-in-Charge of Public Works, Bangsamoro Government Center, Cotabato City, the herein \"Request of Construction of Multi-Purpose Building, Construction of Covered Court, Patrol Vehicle, Construction of Water System at Barangay Polloc, Parang, Maguindanao del Norte\"., Parang, ,', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Zd-qnICPAeS7yqUeter4XJ5E0cpJjbrT/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- consider for FF.', ''),
(3669, '', '2024-12-26', 'ZOHRIA\'S. BANSI-GURO  - Municipal Mayor', 'MDN - I am writing your good office pertaining to the approved road project in your office particularly at Sitio Campo Uno in Barangay Sapad which the undersigned is proposing for its re-alignment to other area of the same barangay, more or less 1 kilometer from the original site. The original site of the project is already being constructed by the Provincial Government of Maguindanao Del Norte. Thus, prompting this office in proposing for the re-alignment of the road project.\n\n, Matanog, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BzBwt4wVsiWa2_oQxSVK5dhu7PAwmJcu/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- verify funding of project', ''),
(3670, '', '2024-12-26', 'ENGR. BAI TAYAN. MANGALANGKAT, MPA  - Engineer III', 'MDN - The Datu Blah T. Sinsuat District Hospital, located in Brgy. Nuro, Upi, Maguindanao Del Norte, serves as a vital healthcare facility for the surrounding communities. Recently upgraded to a 100-bed capacity Level 2 hospital through the Bangsamoro Autonomy Act No. 25, our hospital is committed to improving and expanding its services to meet the growing healthcare needs of the population.\nIn addition, the Province of Maguindanao Del Norte, headed by Governor Abdulra of Macacua, \nWe respectfully request your support in improving a total of 1 kilometer of two-lane roads with shouldering within and around our facility, as detailed below:\nROAD A- From the National Highway to Brgy. Road of Biarong (200 meters)\nROAD B-From Road A to the COVID Facility Road (100 meters)\nROAD C-From COVID Facility Road to the Operating Room (OR) Building (100 meters)\nROAD D - From the Activity Area to the Laundry Building (100 meters)\nROAD E-Surrounding the COVID Facility (350 meters)\nROAD F-From the Generator House to the Dieta, ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tgWPhq0-qYxnWh7j8vNa_EBQ-3W8Fqwr/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- memo to deo to validate', ''),
(3671, '', '2024-12-27', 'NASSIE BMARUHOM  - Municipal Mayor of Marogong', 'MDN - As the BARMM emerges to thrive and oath to lead and live for moral governance, we, your constituent are requesting your kind approval to our request project which is Concreting of Farm to Market Road (FMR) From Brgy. Balut - Brgy. Piangologan, Marogong, Lanao Del Sur.\n\nMOHAMAD \"DIMAS\" S. ADAM\nDeputy Brigade Commander (GHQ-BIAF)\n\n, Marogong, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FIMfe8ABDCYhxtPLd0r7L91KGwBFWk9x/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Memo to deo to validate', ''),
(3672, '', '2024-12-27', 'BUTCH MALANG - Chairman MILF-CCCH', 'MDN - I am respectfully asking your good office an allocation of funds for the Construction of Concrete RC Pipe or Box Culvert and 600 meter Road Concreting Municipal Road at Brgy. Macabiso, Sultan Mastura, Maguindanao del Norte. The collection support for the promotion of Moral Governance from Brgy. Macabiso, Sultan Mastura, Maguindanao del Norte and its people is expressed through this letter. Considering your strong advocacy for community development, I believe that your support will make a significant difference in enhancing our community at large.\n\n, Sultan Mastura, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MeeQTUwKB15Zv3ZTq4wMV18WBa4ct_aq/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Maybe consider under sdf', '');
