(3673, '', '2024-12-27', 'ABDELLA A. SAAD   - Brgy. Chairman', 'LDS2 - I am writing to seek your consideration of our proposed projects aimed at enhancing the community facilities in Brgy. Romagondong, Marogong, Lanao Del Sur. The proposed projects are as follows:\r\n1. FMR Concreting;\r\n2. Water System; and\r\n3. Cover Court\r\n\r\nMOHAMAD \"DIMAS\" S. ADAM \r\nDeputy Brigade Commander (GHQ-Base Command), Marogong, , ', '', 'Communication(External)', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/11rDhuJ0Y-V-EyUyHnyciDn9K3xvqYjiE/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- See above instruction', ''),
(3674, '', '2024-12-27', 'CASANALIM. BOROBORO   - Brgy Chairman', 'LDS2 - I am writing to seek your consideration of our proposed projects aimed at enhancing the community facilities in Brgy Calumbog, Marogong, Lanao Del Sur. The proposed projects are as follows:\n1. Water System Level II;\n2. Covered Court; and\n3. Brgy. Concreting;\n\nMOHAMAD \"DIMAS\" S. ADAM \nDeputy Brigade Commander (GHQ-Base Command, Marogong, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PmBnE7cTQm8EjsrbKP3SelPuFkZs8l3Z/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- verify funding', ''),
(3675, '', '2024-12-27', 'ÃRAB M. ABI  - Brgy. Chairman', 'LDS2 - I am writing to seek your consideration of our proposed projects aimed at enhancing the community facilities in Brgy. Macao, Balabagan, Lanao Del Sur. The proposed projects are as follows:\r\n1. Water System Level II; and\r\n2. Covered Court\r\nALEEM B. TAMANO\r\nDeputy on Expeditionary Mission 115th Base Command Western Mindanao Front BIAF-MILF, Balabagan, , ', '', 'Communication(External)', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1UDLEz_RWh3NSV9Tzhiv2kAE-_AfOm3A2/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- see above instruction', ''),
(3676, '', '2025-01-02', 'Esmael \"Paolo\" Kuman,  - Chairman', 'MDS - Respectfully endorsing to your good office the request of Municipal Chairman Esmael \"Paolo\" Kuman, MILF Political Committee, for the construction and concreting of 2.8 kilometers that will cover roads leading to Sittio katidtuan, Brgy Makainis, Gen. Salipada K. Pendatun.\nRAFSANJANI P. ALI Municipal Mayor\nLMP-Prcoident\nLAMPADA K. PENDATUN, MAG.\nMaguindanao del Sur Chapter, Gen. Salipada K. Pendatun., , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1LrKyDyabNN0MwUFnsQNOA9g0f33ETAFv/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- memo to deo to validate if unfunded', ''),
(3677, '', '2025-01-02', 'KEPEG M. MATIO  - Brigade Commander', 'SGA - I am writing to seek your consideration of our proposed projects aimed at enhancing the community facilities in Sitio Bungalos, Brgy Kabasalan, Ligawasan, SGA. The proposed projects are as follows:\n1. Road Concreting;\n2. Covered Court;\n3. Water System Level II;\n\nKEPEG M. MATIO\nBrigade Commander\n\nSITTIE M. KAMBANG Mun. Councilor\n7th Brigade, (National Guard Front) Ligawasan Municipality\n\nABDUL BASSEIR K. ALI\nIA President\nSitio Lidasan IA\n#: 09067029456, Ligawasan, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ChZBcfuNLNTJCQft07jB310vIn2PJ612/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- consider in sdf FF', ''),
(3678, '', '2025-01-02', 'AMENODEN 1. COSAIN   - Brgy. Chairman', 'LDS2 - I am writing to seek your consideration of our proposed projects aimed at enhancing the community facilities in Brgy. Bolawan, Marogong, Lanao Del Sur. The proposed projects are as follows:\n1. FMR Concreting: (Gandamato - Camp Akeraker); and\n2. Hanging Bridge (100 Ln.m)\n\nAMENODEN 1. COSAIN \nBrgy. Chairman\n\nAMER B. SARIP\nBrgy. Official\nMOHAMAD DIMAS\" S. ADAM Deputy Brigade Commander (GHQ-Base Command), Marogong, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1qRi9e4TngmKop9pw2YzxYKuqHtLfncYE/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- memo to deo to validate', ''),
(3679, '', '2025-01-02', 'AJAN S. AJIJUL   - District Engineer', 'SUL1 - In connection to the projects funded to Municipality of Hji Panglima Tahil, Sulu. We have been observed recently that the budget for FY 2025 RI under this municipality have greatly reduced and this would cause a negative impact to the area might be left behind in the development. In line with this, we are respectfully requesting from you to please include this following project proposals (Attached list & geotagged photo) of this municipality.\nWe are hoping for your positive response regarding this matter.\nThank you very much.\n\n\nAJAN S. AJIJUL \nDistrict Engineer, Sulu, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/14yVtVBBxPpBJJauLCXRMf3-HDydB7GDl/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify proposals', ''),
(3680, '', '2025-01-02', 'BHEN ZAR M. AMIROL  - Brigade Commander', 'MDS - \nSubject: Request for the Construction of Water System in Barangay Kakar, Datu Odin Sinsuat, Maguindanao del Norte\nDear Honorable Minister Guerra:\n\nBHEN ZAR M. AMIROL \nBrigade Commander\nNoted by:\nAshimbar\nHON. ASNAWI \"JOJO\" S. LIMBONA Former Board Member\nMaguindanao del Norte, Datu Odin Sinsuat, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1QD0makITfpZtFX9Yt8uZdh8oTPjH1HFf/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- consider for FF', ''),
(3681, '', '2025-01-02', 'ZOHRIA S. BANSIL-GURO  - Mayor', 'MDN - \nAs we now try hard to develop our municipality from being once an embattled and impoverished municipality being host to waves of armed-confrontation between the moro resistance organizations (MNLF/MILF) against the Armed Forces of the Philippine Government from 60s until the early part of year 2000, much are still needed to be done in order to transform the narrative of Matanog \"from War Zone to Eco Zone\".\nAlong this line, may we request two (2) important subprojects through your good office for funding assistance for the following priority projects, to wit:\n1. Construction of One (1) Unit Covered Court at Sitio Smart Tower, Bayanga Norte \n2. Concrete Pavement of One (1) Km Sitio Pril - Lawaan - Basak FMR, Langkong\nShould you wish, you may reach us through our person in charge, Mr. Ponpon Zaman with Contact No. 0915-165-3959.\n\n\n\n, Matanog, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pf_iktMgH9dujjW6jzAjC573eKdCPFmW/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- memo to deo', ''),
(3682, '', '2025-02-10', 'KHALIDA D/POLAO-SANGUILA  - Municipal Mayor', 'LDS2 - REQUEST FOR REALIGNMENT OF BARANGAY PAIGOAY BRIDGE INTO KALAGITASAN BRIDGE IN BARANGAY BANGON PAGAYAWAN, LANAO DEL SUR PROJECT FY 2025, PAGAYAWAN, ,', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/15vILNhn_64pKfogyDkc0qCJnC_6sgs1I/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- See above instruction', ''),
(3683, '', '2025-02-16', 'HON. NORMAN C. INALANG,  - OIC-MAYOR OF KAPALAWAN', 'SGA - \na letter signed by HON. NORMAN C. INALANG, OIC-MAYOR OF KAPALAWAN, SGA of the Bangsamoro Autonomous Region in Muslim Mindanao REQUESTING ASSISTANCE IN ESTABLISHING A WATER SUPPLY SYSTEM FOR THE KAPALAWAN MUNICIPAL HALL (Temporary Government Center) with further information stated in the attached letter., Kapalawan, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Uiopp8BNVaI7cRo2OmqK-lD55YfVtnIx/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- for consideration in FY 2026', ''),
(3684, '', '2025-02-16', 'Shiek Alimudin Adam - Proponent', 'SGA - \nWe in Bario Mulanta Tonganon Near Tupig Kapalawan Municipality, are requested or asking for help to install a\nwater supply and water tank as well, for the reason that the people\'s sources of drinking water are too far away.\nYour response is very important and\nhelpful to us.\nvery\nAllah Bless you more Thank you very much\nShiek Alimudin Adam\nadamsal865@gmail.com 09068457253, Kapalawan, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1NoO3d-iqAzBz5INMLRFnNAFb0XWYvd4R/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify if attached location map is unfunded', ''),
(3685, '', '2025-02-16', 'DATU UMBRA B. DILANGLEN  - Municipal Mayor', 'MDN - \nThis pertains to the request of the Municipality of Northern Kabuntalan, Maguindanao del Norte in the amount of Seventy-Five Million Pesos (PhP 75,000,000.00) for the following infrastructure projects:\nParticulars\n1. Construction of Evacuation Center\n2. Construction of Flood Control and Riverbank Protection at Barangay Gayonga and Barangay Sabaken\n\n\n, Northern Kabuntalan, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1U8Fd00yczj28L99yEjcTJKrE0wbdQDDD/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Endore Evac center to MILG', ''),
(3686, '', '2025-02-16', 'IBRAHIM M. RUMUMBA, -  Barangay Chairman', 'MDN - Respectfully transmitting to DANILO A. ONG, Officer-in-Charge, Ministry of Public Works (MPW)-BARMM, the herein endorsement from ALVIN-YASHER K. ABDULGAFAR, Chief of Staff, Office of the Chief Minister (OCM)-BARMM, the herein letter from IBRAHIM M. RUMUMBA, Barangay Chairman of Barangay Oring, Municipality of Buldon, Province of Maguindanao del Norte, requesting funding assistance for the construction of one (1) kilometer farm-to-market road, one (1) unit multi-purpose building, and one (1) unit warehouse with solar dryer in Barangay Oring., Buldon, ,', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1lANgQXHUEjICS_ChSydQuGhlPnvhKFJg/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify road funding', ''),
(3687, '', '2025-02-16', 'ANDY B. AL-SAMO,  - Barangay Chairman', 'MDN - \nRespectfully transmitting to DANILO A. ONG, Officer-in-Charge, Ministry of Public Works (MPW)-BARMM, the herein endorsement from ALVIN-YASHER K. ABDULGAFAR, Chief of Staff, Office of the Chief Minister (OCM)-BARMM, the herein letter from ANDY B. AL-SAMO, Barangay Chairman of Barangay Ampuan, Municipality of Buildon, Province of Maguindanao del Norte, requesting funding assistance for the construction of one (1) kilometer farm-to-market, one (1) unit multipurpose building, and one (1) unit warehouse with solar dryer in Barangay Ampuan., Buldon, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/12c7P1Zpeousuf1cOLGc7LnoX-1KltlZl/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Endorse MPB to MILG', ''),
(3688, '', '2025-02-16', 'DATUMANONG DILAWANEN - Proponent', 'OSB - \nRespectfully transmitting to DANILO A. ONG, Officer-in-Charge, Ministry of Public Works (MPW)-BARMM, the herein endorsement from ALVIN-YASHER K. ABDULGAFAR, Chief of Staff, Office of the Chief Minister (OCM)-BARMM, the herein letter from PRESIDENTIAL ACTION CENTER with PACE Code No. PM-GDP-10-30- 2024-047, relative to the communication from DATUMANONG DILAWANEN, requesting the following:\n1. Three (3) units of ten (10) wheeler dump trucks;\n2. One (1) unit of backhoe; and\n3. One (1) unit of large grader., Equipments, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/17MKnOai7gS7AbPDt_ow33VUVj7PQOwpc/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Draft Response letter to OCM', ''),
(3689, '', '2025-02-16', 'Hon. Allanodin m. Guro  - Punong barangay', 'LDS1 - \nAssalamo alaikom... and good day to you. Thank you for your propt response to my request for assistance in concreating the 200-meter road segment in barangay Mipantao Gadongan, maraei city.\nI understand that my request will be reffered to the ministry of public works for appropriate action.\nMay I kindly request for a timeline or estimated timeframe for when can expect an update or feedback from the Ministry of Public Works regarding my request?\nI am eager to follow up on this matter and ensure that the neccesary steps are taken to improve the road infrastructure in our barangay.\nThank you for your time and attention in this matter.\nSincerely,\nHon. Allanodin m. Guro\nPunong barangay\nBrgy. Mipantao gadongan\nMarawi city\n0955 143 5438\n, Marawi City, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tkhIl6cGO3vRE0l7PwRKg_CYfTMQEXw1/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify status of said proposal', ''),
(3690, '', '2025-02-16', 'ANWAR Z. SALUWANG,  - Municipal Mayor,', 'SGA - \nRespectfully transmitting to DANILO A. ONG, Officer-in-Charge, Ministry of Public Works (MPW)-BARMM, the herein endorsement from ALVIN-YASHER K. ABDULGAFAR, Chief of Staff, Office of the Chief Minister (OCM)-BARMM, the herein letter from HON. ANWAR Z. SALUWANG, Municipal Mayor, Municipality of Nabalawag, Special Geographic Area-BARMM, submitting the following Sangguniang Bayan resolutions:\n1. Sangguniang Bayan Resolution No. 2024-022 entitled \"A RESOLUTION RESPECTFULLY REQUESTING THE OFFICE OF HONORABLE OIC MINISTER DANILO A. ONG, MINISTRY OF PUBLIC WORKS, BARMM COMPOUND, COTABATO CITY TO ALLOCATE FUNDS FOR THE CONSTRUCTION OF A 6.6 KM MEGA DIKE WITH SOLAR POWERED PUMP AMOUNTING TO P1.452B FOR THE MUNICIPALITY OF NABALAWAG\"; and\n2. Sangguniang Bayan Resolution No. 2024-027 entitled \"A RESOLUTION RESPECTFULLY REQUESTING THE MINISTRY OF AGRICULTURE, FISHERIES AND AGRARIAN REFORM (MAFAR) TO ALLOCATE FUNDS FOR THE CONCRETING OF FARM TO MARKET ROAD (FMR) FROM THE CENTER OF BARANGAY DAMATULAN TO SITIO SAMALA', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ayeq2itm8XBxM43m8tVu3pK3Di_14eiV/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Endorse mega dike to BPDA', ''),
(3691, '', '2025-02-16', 'MUKTAR S. TULINO,  - Barangay Chairman,', 'MDS - \nRespectfully transmitting to DANILO A. ONG, Officer-in-Charge, MPW- BARMM, the attached three (3) separate letters dated 11 November 2024 from MUKTAR S. TULINO, Barangay Chairman, Barangay Andavit, Datu Salibo, Maguindanao del Sur, regarding the request for assistance for the following projects:\n1. Water System Project (Level 2/Potable Water);\n2. Construction of 1.3km Farm-to-Market Road; and\n3. Flood Control Project., Datu Salibo, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1jqx4DMOTNjasqNujstfEpvl_aF3gLs9u/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify fund; memo to deo', ''),
(3692, '', '2025-02-16', 'MOHAMAD AL BANGELEN  - Punong Barangay', 'COT - \nThe residents of Barangay Anding S. Lim, Poblacion 1, Cotabato City, Special Province, BARMM, is badly need of Government projects like Concreting of Roads and Multi-Purpose Covered Court..\nIn line with the foregoing, I am respectfully requesting your good I office to provide my Barangay in Cotabato City with these projects in order to cater the request of individuals. I am looking forward that we could work as partner in delivering these basic social services to my constituents in the Barangay Anding S. Lim, Pobalcion 1, Cotabato City, Special Province, BARMM.\n\nMOHAMAD AL BANGELEN\nPunong Barangay\nPobalcion 1, Cotabato City\n09176274356, Cotabato City, , ', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1G1Gpu-Gog1HQyCQu3HGGHXNB01UKCUtc/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Memo to DEO', ''),
