(4262, '', '2024-09-11', 'BTA', 'Submitting herewith the attached copy of my project proposal, under my Transitional Development Impact Fund. 2 units of Multi-Purpose Building (20.00m x 8.00) 160sq.m with furniture\'s. 1 unit Covered Court (20.00m x 30.00m) 360sq.m with concrete posts. 2 units of Barangay Road/FMR Concreting of 250 meters length, 5 meters width and 0.20 meters / 8 inches thickness road. 2 packages of Solar Street Lights 25 Units - 60 Watts Solar Powered LED Lights with 3\" Diameter Galvanized Steel Pipe Post and Concrete Pedestal and 1 package of One Storey Two (2) Classrooms School Building in Basic and Madaris Education The project consists of: a.2 classrooms with student armchairs b. 2 set of Teacher\'s table and chair c. 2 whiteboard/blackboard suitable for the classroom d. 8 units of ceiling fan e. 2 common toilets for men and women.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PQQfaq97U7KLQuGGOVCUrLpKeVaGmzFy/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Prep. Response OFFICE OF MP ALBAKIL D. JIKIRI', ''),
