(4299, '', '2024-09-30', 'BTA', 'Request for the realignment of location of our One Hundred (100) meters Concrete Footbridge Project from Barangay Bantek, Upi to be transferred at Barangay Sedem, Datu Blah Sinsuat both within Maguindanao del Norte for the reason that the nature design of the said project is not applicable to Barangay Bantek because everytime when a heavy downpour of rain comes, the high-level of floodwater could reach the footbridge and might destroy it. The aforementioned project is amounting to Four Million Pesos (Php 4,000,000.00) and is under the Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) for the FY 2023 of our office.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1XbAmqn6CLdW-J9Q5C6j47Ff3r8jEkgb3/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- FAA; MP HON. MORAMON A. PIANG, SR', ''),
