(4315, '', '2024-09-30', 'LDS1', 'I hope this letter finds you in good health. I am writing to inform you about an important development concerning the proposed basketball court project in Barangay Patani under former MP Jamel \"James\" D. Macaraya\'s TDIF project. Due to the increasing frequency of flooding in the proposed site during rainy days, which has been exacerbated by climate change, we have found it necessary to reconsider the location of the project. After careful assessment, it has been determined that continuing with the project in the current site poses significant risks to the infrastructure project. To ensure the success and longevity of this project, we have decided to transfer the site of the basketball court to Barangay Gadongan, Marawi City, which offers a more stable location.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Gk_2S3iTmzbilvB4BjmSb-D4t7u5IrgH/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Check the status of the project', ''),
