(4382, '', '2024-10-25', 'MHSD', 'In line with this, the Ministry proudly joins the National Shelter Month celebration by hosting its 3rd Annual Policy Agenda Forum, titled \"Strengthening Inclusive Housing and Settlement Policies for a Sustainable Bangsamoro Community.\" The event will be held on October 29, 2024, at Em Manor Hotel and Convention Center, Cotabato City. This forum aims to bring together key stakeholders to explore and enhance policies that promote inclusive and sustainable housing solutions in the Bangsamoro region, contributing to the broader goal of nation-building.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1I3-Uaa3hR2uByhrHxhPT-oEqehfk88Za/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Kindly Attend', ''),
