(4437, '', '2024-11-20', 'COT', 'On behalf of my neighbors & me in Rosales St, Barangay Rosary Heights 6, we would like to seek your assistance regarding our street which until now was never repaired by the local government unit of Cotabato. We sent a letter to Mayor Bruce Matabalao last 2022, and until now we got no reply except to send me a message through his FB page that the city roads are now under the office of MPW, BARMM. So we waited for so long but decided to seek your help this time. Rosales Street was once a pleasant and safe place to live. The poor condition of the road & a busy street now being used as entry & exit of various cars, trucks & buses in/outgoing to Cotabato City via Diversion Road, added more injury to the present condition of the street.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Iu2m8WlHlCSxGawcl7Zgv4G7bF1VoFlw/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Prepare memo to CCDEO..', ''),
