(4444, '', '2024-12-26', 'BPDA', 'We are pleased to provide you with a copy of the Bangsamoro Rehabilitation and Recovery Plan (BRRP) 2023-2028 With Financing and Investment Requirements for STS Paeng Affected Communities, approved by the Bangsamoro Disaster Risk Reduction and Management Council (BDRRMC) on February 1, 2024.\nWe appreciate your ministry\'s efforts in making this plan a reality, along with the support of our development partners from the World Bank.\nAlso, we kindly request your esteemed Ministry to provide us with your email address so we can send a soft copy of the BRRP 2023-2028 for STS Paeng.\nIf you have any questions or need more clarification, please contact Ms. Majah Candao at mobile number +639158882508 or via email ppossd.bpda@gmail.com. We eagerly anticipate your timely response.\nThank you for your continued support and commitment to the Bangsamoro.\nVery truly yours,\nENGR. MOHAJIRIN T. ALI, MNSA\nBangsamoro Director General, BPDA and\nVice-Chairperson, Rehabilitation and Recovery, BDRRMC', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/10qDtZlRhxHqpHC_UFsgG3U7cShYrmj9h/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Prepare response letter', ''),
