(4449, '', '2024-12-26', 'BTA', 'Subject: Request for a copy of Programs, Activities and Projects\nThis is to formally request from your good office a copy of the Programs, Activities and Projects of your good Ministry for the calendar year 2023.\nThe purpose of this request is to be used as a material reference for the drafting of a hill that aims to improve the services and assistance of the Bangsamoro Government to Bangsamoro communities in the outside of the Bangsamoro Region.\nHUSSE PUÃ‘OZ\nMember of Parliament\nBangsamoro Transition Authority (BTA)', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/127JE4B5LNhoWpuNZBiF36PjQXbog0nAd/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Prep. Request data', ''),
