(4456, '', '2024-12-26', 'DPWH', 'The Asian Development Bank (ADB) will hold a Training Workshop for the Integrated Flood Resilience Adaptation (InFRA1) Project, focusing on ADB Safeguards and Gender covering priority projects for Abra, Tagum-Libuganon and Ranao (Agus) River Basins. This workshop aims to enhance participants\' understanding of key environmental and social safeguards and gender considerations essential for the successful implementation of the InFRA1 project.\nIn this regard, we would like to invite two (2) representatives from your office to participate the workshop on November 18-19, 2024, at the Acacia Hotel, JP Laurel Ave., Lanang, Davao City, Davao Del Sur. Attached are the letter dated October 30, 2024 of ADB and the draft agenda for your reference.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1V8s4wtySqdGLzdhQPkTG8-kSOXQOgPP1/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- kindly attend', ''),
