(4478, '', '2025-01-02', 'RO', 'This pertains to the project proposals submitted by various Local Government Units (LGUs), the Moro Islamic Liberation Front (MILF), Moro National Liberation Front (MNLF), and other stakeholders to the SDF-PMO for possible funding undor the Special Development Fund (SDF) for FY 2025.\nAnent this, we are officially endorsing the consolidated project proposals to your office for review, evaluation, and inclusion in your programming and budgeting processes. We respectfully request that, following your review, the evaluated list of proposals be returned to the SDF-PMO for further consideration and potential funding under FY 2025 SDF along with your regular proposals for FY 2026 GAAB and FY 2025 SDF for alignment with future funding opportunities.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Qrtcy5SEuQlGizQvriEPe5DKJP_QZV7Q/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- verify if unfunded;', ''),
