(4531, '', '2025-02-14', 'TDIF', 'I hope this letter finds you well. This is in line with the Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) project of our office, specifically the Construction of Covered Court - Option 2 at Picong, Lanao Del Sur. Previously, we had requested it to be transferred at Datu Piang, Maguindanao Del Sur.\nFurther, we would like to inform you that we would like to cancel the said transfer of the project location. We would like to retain it at its original project location, which is at Picong, Lanao Del Sur.\n\nABDULWAJAB M. PAK Member of Parliament\n', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1b-k9Ut4ipuwAelhFTCpBe_8R_IPUtw13/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- for info file', ''),
