(4536, '', '2025-02-14', 'BTA', 'In reference to the letter submitted last August 7, 2024 regarding the modifications of my TDIF 2023 Proposed Project entitled Construction of Davao Cultural Center worth P5,000,000.00. We decided to forego the initially proposed location due to unavailability of the land at Escandor Rd., Brgy., Zone III, Sta. Cruz, Davao del Sur. Anent this, due to the willingness of constituents to donate a land at Brgy. Clib, Hagonoy, Davao del Sur, we decided to modify the location of the project to the aforementioned location.\nI sincerely hope you will give this some positive thought.\nShukran.\nHON. HUS LIY MUNOZ Member of the Parliament', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1C6DZkrRHwx1NzbDjK8lOSe3rHB5R42Bs/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- is this same location same as the initial request', ''),
