(4539, '', '2025-02-15', 'BAS', 'We are writing to formally justify the decision to shorten the planned length of the road from 1.00km to .72km of 22-TD35BN093 Concreting of Barangay Road/FMR, Sitio Patugu, Brgy. Guinanta, Al-Barka, Basilan due to budget constraints. This adjustment was made after a thorough review of project costs and available funding, and it reflects our commitment to responsible budget management while still achieving essential project goals. During the planning and budgeting phases, we identified that the estimated cost for the original project length exceeded the available budget allocation.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1MWmPHbwcYizmjVbkqUqa9_SP7Bpwsbgn/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- FAA', ''),
