(4550, '', '2025-02-16', 'BTA', '\nThis is to submit this letter to comply with the corrected locations for the Solar Streetlight Project under my 2024 Transitional Development Impact Fund, as requested. This letter serves as an update to our previous submission dated September 25, 2024, to ensure accuracy in the specified project locations.\nBrgy. Bacayawan, Marantao, Purok 1\nBrgy. Bacayawan, Marantao, Purok 2\nBrgy. Tacub Pindolonan, Marantao, Purok 1\nBrgy. Tacub Pindolonan, Marantao, Purok 2 Brgy. Bubong Camalig\nBrgy. Pagalongan Bacayawan, Marantao, Purok 1\nBrgy. Pagalongan Bacayawan, Marantao, Purok 2\nWe kindly request that these updated locations be considered to facilitate timely implementation of the project. For any further clarification, please do not hesitate to contact our TDIF Focal Person, Samsodin M. Sigayan, at 0927-490-9987 or via email at mpjamramos@gmail.com.\n\nDIAMILA DISIMBAN-RAMOS Member of Parliament', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1tysCPStqEaEFHV-da2-76NncZY6-gpu0/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify fund source', ''),
