(4563, '', '2025-02-16', 'BTA', '\n\nThe Office of MP Haron M. Abas requests your Ministry\'s approval to change the recipient of one (1) unit Covered Court under our office\'s TDIF 2023 which we originally allocated for Brgy. Poblacion III to be granted instead to Brgy. Bagua 1 in Cotabato City. During our recent monitoring, the landowner has disallowed the implementation of the project on their property at Brgy. Poblacion III.\nTo ensure the effective utilization of the above-mentioned project, we propose its transfer to a certain and ideal site at Brgy. Bagua I, where it will provide significant benefits to the community.\nShould you have questions or clarifications, you may contact our focal person at 09451531388 or via email at mpharonmabas.office@gmail.com.\n\nHON. HARON M. ABAS Member of the Parliament\n', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yTUQ1uye1hoibw-eBAhCBXDAzNxg_-QV/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- verify current status', ''),
(4564, '', '2025-02-16', 'BTA', '\nPlease be informed that the one (1) unit Covered Court (option-2) under Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) 2023 which originally located at Barangay Mibpandakan GSKP Maguindanao Del Sur will transfer to Barangay Kayaga Municipality of Pandag, Maguindanao Del Sur due to:\n1. There was already 1-unit constructed Covered Court in the said barangay. 2. The new proposed site Barangay Kayaga of Pandag specifically in KAYAGA INTEGRATED ACADEMY, INC. \nHON. SAID Z. SALENDAB\nMember of Parliament', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1pv0ahiMU2cp7hG7tSRXcBQtklHxOzfEG/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify Status', ''),
(4565, '', '2025-02-16', 'RO', '\n= Back-To-Office-Report (BTOR) - Joint Validation for the TDIF 2024, SGA\nProjects:\n1. 24-TD6163B091- Construction of Covered Court (Option 2) 2. 24-TD1563B219 - Construction of Warehouse with Solar dryer 3. 24-TD7363B229 - Installation of Solar Street lights, (25 units) 4. 24-TD7363B230 - Installation of Solar Street lights, (25 units)', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ZVP_b_NAfCov2w5_Fecvaro8O187f1Uo/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- prepare status', ''),
