(4569, '', '2025-02-16', 'LDS1', '\nThis is in response to your letter dated March 13, 2024, which we only received via email on November 8, 2024. The requested realignment of our 2023 TDIF project (Construction of Multi-Purpose Building) from Camp Ranao (Beside 103rd Infantry Brigade Military Base), Brgy. Saber, Marawi City, Lanao del Sur to Brgy. Cabingan, Marawi City, Lanao del Sur is driven by several practical and strategic considerations.\n\nAbdulaziz M. Ãmenoden Member of Parliament', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/18g-bfZNux-Z_x17oL4-B3Z1XH_nU6tI4/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Verify status', ''),
(4570, '', '2025-02-16', 'BTA', '\nThis is with reference to Memorandum Order No. 170, dated 11 October 2024, directing this office to conduct a site evaluation of the realigned location of the project proposed by HON. HUSSEIN P. MUÃ‘OZ, Member of Parliament, to validate the feasibility of constructing the project.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1evaxENA_awSurAMXRS4XpTtzd2n4rwVl/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Check attached docs.', ''),
(4571, '', '2025-02-16', 'TAW', '\n1\n23-TD09-TT280\n23-TD09-TT283\n2\n23-TD51-TT147\n3\n14\n24-RITTOI266\n5\n24-RITTP0234\nDETAILS\nConstruction of SULU archipelago learning Institute of culture and heritage building Mindanao state university Tawi-tawi college of technology and oceanography (MSU-TCTO), sanga-sanga Bongao, Tawi-Tawi\nconstruction of sea wall/waterbreak pahut, Bongao, Tawi-tawi\nInstallation of Solar Street light Boheh Sallang, Sanga-sanga Bongau, Tawi-tawi\nConstruction of fishport, Brgy. UNGUS-UNGUS, Bongao, Tawi-tawi\nInstallation of Solar Light along footbridge of Tawi-tawi', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Ni_meM5_sWEfAWs87JKefFh-0nLWeSYq/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- FAA', ''),
(4572, '', '2025-02-16', 'SL1', '\nWe are hereby submitting the request of MP MATARUL M. ESTINO for the \"Reconstruction of Sition Tanjung, Brgy. Kajatian Port, Brgy. Kajatian, Indanan, Sulu\". Attached are the letter from the Office of MP Matarul M. Estino provided with Validation report with POW and plan prepared by this district,', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/19iGp2rOC--x-LSxn19h6vffmL0QVl1h4/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- verify if considered in previous validation', ''),
