(4574, '', '2025-02-16', 'BPDA', '1. The Regional Land Use Committee (RLUCom) will conduct its \"3rd Regular Meeting for CY 2024 on Wednesday, 13 November 2024, 8:30 a.m. at the BPDA Conference Hall 2, Bangsamoro Government Center, Cotabato City.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1T3aL5RYsKHSzvP26zWnJ3qlxc7MU9zwH/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Check docs', ''),
(4575, '', '2025-02-16', 'MINDA', '\nWe are pleased to invite your technical team to the 21st Mindanao Development Corridors- Joint Planning and Programming (MinDC-JPP) Session for Roads, Bridges, and Flood Control Projects on November 20, 2024 in Manila to discuss the status of the MinDC-JPP priority interregional projects in Mindanao.\nSpecifically, may we request BARMM through BPDA and MPW to present the following: a) status of priority interregional road and flood control projects in the BARMM; b) MinDC-JPP *projects embedded in the CY 2025 NEP: c) projects proposed in the CY 2026 AIP and d) issues and concerns on the project identification, development and implementation in BARMM in coordination with DPWH Regional Offices and the RPMO. Attached is the program flow and template of the presentation, for your reference.\nFor any queries or clarification, please feel free to contact our staff member, Ms. Madania P. Malang-Casinto, at her mobile number 0917-126-4986 or email address madania.malang@minda.gov.ph.\n\nSECRE', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1aDUvqMc4-BhtlNQ2bklAFEVkf2XkrXIx/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Coordinate with the  MINDA focal', ''),
(4576, '', '2025-02-16', 'SGA', '\nWe in Bario Mulanta Tonganon Near Tupig Kapalawan Municipality, are requested or asking for help to install a water supply and water tank as well, for the reason that the people\'s sources of drinking water are too far away.\nYour response is very important and very helpful to us. Allah Bless you more Thank you very much\nShiek Alimudin Adam\nadamsal865@gmail.com 09068457253', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1WvXrr27_DxvCMFgQSITKAs8UL10MvvIH/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- prev. funding consolidate', ''),
