(4579, '', '2025-02-16', 'MDN', '\nOn behalf of the Local Government of Datu Blah Sinsuat (DBS), I would like to formally invite you to attend the Public Hearing on the Comprehensive Land Use Plan (CLUP) for the Fiscal Year 2024-2034 of our municipality. The hearing is scheduled for December 3, 2024, at 10:00 AM, and will take place at the 2nd Floor, Legislative Building, Barangay Pura, Datu Blah Sinsuat, Maguindanao del Norte.\n\nPlease confirm your attendance on or before November 29, 2024. If you are unable to attend, written feedback or comments are welcome, or you can text or call at Cellphone Number 09557168327 before the hearing.\n\nDATU MARSHALL SINSUAT\nMunicipal Mayor', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GuI6nFO7qx1Jau32B4cioqCZpuotzQPq/view?usp=sharing', '', '', '- Contact MDN PPD Chief', ''),
