(4627, '', '2025-02-23', 'BTA', 'Assalamu\'alaikum wa rahmatullahi wa barakatuh.This is in reference to the communication that our office forwarded to MPW on submission of the revised Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) 2025 proposed projects of the Office of MP. Atty. Jet Lim, Al-Haj, MNSA.Kindly note that we initially included the two (2) proposed projects under MPW, purchase of wheel type excavator and the construction of two (2) footbridges, in the the menu list to be funded and implemented under TDIF 2024 budget.As we have decided to transfer those projects for funding and implementation under TDIF 2025 budget, we therefore would like to respectfully request your office to cancel the proposed projects under TDIF 2024 that we initially submitted.Kindly refer to the attached documents for copies of transmittal of our revised TDIF list for references. Should you require any further clarifications, feel free to contact our office at 0956-854-6611 or via email at officeofmplim@bta.gov.ph and mp.jetlim@gmail.com', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/14kT13TPXRlI61GEdIwaG1ykWalwhxVOn/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC/RCM - FAA', ''),
