(4682, '', '2025-01-27', 'SUL1', 'We are glad to inform that the beneficiary of the TDIF 2024 lunit of dump truck allocated for members of the parliament is the constituents of Barangay Tubig Dakulah, Municipality of Indanan, Province of Sulu. The incumbent Punong Barangay is the Honorable Alman Uding. MP DENMARTIN A. KAHALAN, PhD', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1PUGmfAC6OjcB7sV1gdiTCb3detAiyBA-/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC - FAA', ''),
(4683, '', '2025-01-27', 'LDS2', 'We are pleased to formally endorse the beneficiary of the 1 Unit Dump Truck from the Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) 2024 for this office. The beneficiary is hereby named:Hon. Anisah P. Macadato, Brgy. Chairman of Sandab, Municipality of Butig, Province of Lanao del sur. MARJANIE S. MIMBANTAS MACASALONG\nMember of Parliament', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1BTxPOS2Hhl26wkHZHtMuc8V-MSNzOXIf/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC - FAA', ''),
(4684, '', '2025-01-27', 'MDN', 'I hope this letter finds you well. This is to submit to you respectfully the beneficiary of our 1- unit Dump Truck allocated from GAAB 2024. In the service of Bangsamoro, the said equipment will be given to the BLGU of Barangay Calsada, Sultan Kudarat, Maguindanao Del Norte to develop their agricultural operations for their community.OFFICE OF MP SUHARTO S. ESMAEL, MSc', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1KZ7T6sLBLKr64q46NkKMRIens1aacc9r/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC - FAA', ''),
