(4686, '', '2025-01-27', 'LDS1', 'In the previous budget hearing of the MPW, the ministry manifested that they are allotting 1 Unit of Dump Truck to each Member of the Parliament sourced from the General Appropriations Act of the Bangsamoro 2024 (GAAB 2024). Having said that, may we request for the immediate release of 1 Unit of Dump Truck for Barangay Kili-Kili East, Wao, Lanao del Sur. This truck will be beneficial in transporting various materials for construction, waste collection and other projects of the barangay.OFFICE OF HON. ATTY. JOSE I. LORENA', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1rR5kPwJCCtnq9y7-JdNMd74BQHwe4LKr/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC - FAA', ''),
