(4743, '', '2025-03-07', 'BTA', 'I am writing to bring to your attention an error in the address that was submitted with our covered court (option 1) project proposal under the 2024 TDIF supplemental budget. It has come to our attention that the address provided in the original submission was incorrect.We sincerely apologize for any confusion or inconvenience this may have caused and would like to request a correction to the address listed in the proposal to ensure smooth communication and coordination moving forward. The correct address for the proposed construction site is Buadi Itowa, Marawi City.We appreciate your understanding and assistance in updating the records accordingly. If there are any further steps or procedures we need to follow to amend this error, please do not hesitate to inform us.SAID. SHIEKMember of the Parliament', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1fAPXhBhepg498oZiznysRgoZY3F-V6Gh/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - FAA', ''),
