(4761, '', '2025-01-27', 'MDN', '\nI respectfully Endorsing to your good office a requested project of SUKARNO A. SAMAD for Sitio Upper Serumfarey Barangay Kinitaan, Municipality of Upi, Maguindanao Del Norte. Which is WAREHOUSE equipped with SOLAR DRYER.\nSaid project will be great help to constituents of the above mentioned area as this will help the constituents during rainy season drying their agricultural products.\n\nMARS S. MARIANO Punong Barangay', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1mWMy-PdRVHdavxD1rxwtHSSDhcpU_J5P/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - FAA', ''),
(4762, '', '2025-03-27', 'BTA', '\nAs stated in the documents submitted to the ministries regarding projects under F.Y. 2024 Transitional Development Impact Supplemental Fund, I have proposed the installation of twenty-five (25) solar streetlights in Brgy. Saimbangon and another twenty-five (25) in Brgy. Pisak. Both barangays are part of the Municipality of Pata, Province of Sulu.\n\nMP ATTY. NABIL A. TAN\nDeputy Speaker', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1D6XkCFNtSKjv2u1ZQ9qEe_8tg5juVlJc/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - FAA', ''),
(4763, '', '2025-01-27', 'SGA', '\nThe barangay officials consultations have successfully drawn a solution such as ROAD CONSTRUCTION DEVELOPMENT at Barangay Simsiman, Pahamudin SGA BARMM.The construction of this development road will benefit the residents for a convenient transportation to their everyday activities. We are persevere to allocate the project for the sustainability of the residents. With this, we are in a great enthusiasm and earnestly request your benevolent office to fund the Road Development project.\n\nROY A. TALIB\nBarangay Kagawad', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1hTUdf6nWCO7Ep9JUR1zDz-_AAbQ7FwyP/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - For FY 2026 consideration', ''),
