(4768, '', '2025-02-07', 'BPDA', 'On September 10, 2024, the Bangsamoro Planning and Development Authority (BPDA) sent a letter inquiring about the status of implementation of the Programs, Projects, and Activities (PPAS) of all concerned Ministries, Offices, and Agencies (BMOAS) for the affected communities of STS Paeng as proposed in the Bangsamoro Rehabilitation and Recovery Plan (BRRP) 2023-2028. This is in line with the mandate of the BPDA to monitor and evaluate the implementation of all PPAs to ensure its contribution to the strategies, objectives, and goals of the 2nd Bangsamoro Development Plan (BDP), 2023-2028.\nFor any queries or clarification, you may contact our focal Engr. Mo\'men B. Embil of the BPDA at mobile number 09061739838.Thank you and we are hoping for your continued cooperation.Very truly yours \nENGR. MOHAJIRINT. ALI, MNSA Bangsamoro Director General, BPDA and Vice-Chairperson, Rehabilitation and Recovery, BDRMMC', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1yxJDvGwPv5CEBQvsTDz0IpZXmdAltT4z/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'HTM - Coordinate with Maintenance Div.', ''),
