(4795, '', '2025-02-07', 'BPDA', 'As we steadfastly fulfill our commitment to monitor and evaluate all development initiatives in the Bangsamoro region, the Regional Project Monitoring and Evaluation Committee (RPMECom) through BPDA will update the list of programs, projects, and activities (PPAs) for each ministry. This data shall serve as the basis for both desk and field monitoring activities throughout the BARMM in the calendar year 2025.\n\nPlease send the signed copy through email at med.bpdabarmm@gmail.com.\nFor further inquiry, you may contact Ms. Sandra N. Maulana at mobile number 09364901447.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1ydjcwMRJv7lHlFHxzxpbOcTxYa8v6Dwj/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'VAC - Prepare the list.', ''),
