(4950, '', '2025-03-10', 'MDN', 'In this respect, we may request the Bangsamoro Government Technical Team to conduct a Joint Area Rapid Assessment, Validation, and Planning Session for our industry-level Agriculture and Fisheries Project Proposals on Thursday, 13th of March 2025 at Marayag Hilltop, Bayanga Norte, Matanog. Maguindanao Del Norte.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1oeMmrklMwoBN-i4WZuxWD9bSUB-mTy7T/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'PHG - kindly attend', ''),
(4951, '', '2025-03-10', 'LDS1', '\nThis pertains to the Christine Villas Housing Project, located in Brgy. Maria Cristina, Balo-i, Lanao del Norte, which was successfully completed on December 3, 2021. The project consists of 1,000 units, including both 2-storey duplex and single-detached types.\n\nSOTERO C. CATANE\nOIC-District Manager\nBukidnon/Misamis Occidental/Lanao District Office\n', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/11mi4zzn7gDwPQZv7Jd3vWah_BGsLhUz4/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - Endorse to LDS', ''),
(4952, '', '2025-03-10', 'OSB', '\nOfficially endorsing to your good office the herein requested proposed Cultural Center Project from Hon. Gov. Rogelio D. Pacquiao of Sarangani Province, thru, Mr. Osmena Thong Salisipan, Chairman of MILF Provincial Political Committee from Alvin-Yasher K. Abdulgafar, Chief of Staff of the Office of the Chief Minister, BARMM.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1iGVMin3_5LCIIKEOgLqD2Im22M33MGL7/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - See Instruction above. FAA', ''),
(4953, '', '2025-03-10', 'MDN', '\nThis is in reference to your Memorandum Order No. 174-A, series of 2024 re: Conduct of Site Validation for Various Project Proposals under the Jurisdiction of Maguindanao del Norte District Engineering Office. Our office, along with the coordination of the indicated proponents of the proposed projects, conducted an evaluation of the proposed site and validated the feasibility of the location. DE AVILA ABOBAKAR', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1LSX1a00k0L9EDAV5XR6MdQ1pHi6mQcpG/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'RCM - inform DEO use the prescribed validation report template..', ''),
