(5006, '', '2025-03-21', 'BTA', 'I am writing to formally request the relocation of the Barangay Road/ FMR project under Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) Project 2024 initially addressed at Tamontaka IV,Cotabato City to be transferred to Biniruan, Poblacion IX, Cotabato City due to the overlapping of an existing project at the formerly said location. The new address of its location offers significant advantages for successful project completion. This move would greatly improve efficiency and resource allocation. We believe this relocation is crucial for the project\'s overall success by properly stating its address. We kindly request you consider this proposal and look forward to discussing the details further. MP MOHAGHER IQBAL', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/16zphr4jbuIGAAeYl6RDCD00lhB2GZgWG/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'JMJ/RCM - verify status of implementation.', ''),
