(5015, '', '2025-03-24', 'BTA', '\nThis has reference to the dump truck as part of the machineries and equipments of your Ministry funded under 2024 GAAB for the Transitional Development Impact Fund.\nThe dump truck will be donated to the Barangay Local Government Unit of Bagua I. Cotabato City. This dump truck will have a significant and lasting impact, especially in areas that lack proper infrastructure and resources. This will also be beneficial for waste management and cleanliness. MP AIDA SILONGAN', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1FWtS8mQ4_gjFMO73E5Zvapj9vUczt1w4/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC - FAA', ''),
