(5018, '', '2025-05-25', 'BTA', '\nWe respectfully submit this request regarding the allocation of one (1) unit Dump Truck, which will be funded under the General Appropriations Act for Budget Year 2024 (GAAB 2024).\nThe designated beneficiary for this unit is Mr. Maher D. Papandayan of Barangay Rinabor-Dandamun, Municipality of Bayang, Lanao del Sur. This request aims to support the local government\'s efforts to enhance public service and infrastructure development in the community. MP ALI MONTAHA DATU HARON BABAO', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1IddUfKuiIegARXJbspc_YjR9xYQkKfHu/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC/NLA - FAA', ''),
(5019, '', '2025-03-25', 'BTA', '\nThis has reference to the dump truck as part of the machineries and equipments of your Ministry funded under 2024 GAAB.\nThe dump truck will be donated to the Barangay Local Government Unit of Bagua II,\nCotabato City. This dump truck will have a significant and lasting impact, especially in areas that lack proper infrastructure and resources. MP AIDA SILONGAN', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1lZbbGq3J584qXtAWtb2ABSXmmDtbvwKg/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC/NLA - FAA', ''),
