(5106, '', '2025-04-25', 'The world bank', 'Key data gaps in the said systems are investments coming from the BARMM government. In this regard, we would like to invite key members of the Planning Division of your office for a coordination meeting on 29 April 2025, 10:00 AM - 12:00 NN, at Peace Room, OPAPRU Field Office, DPWH Compound, Barangay Awang, Datu Odin Sinsuat, Maguindanao del Norte. This will be in preparation for the incoming Technical Working Group (TWG) on Camps Monitoring meeting to be held in May 2025.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1GytnNGEe0iOzf0tIbW2zLlcY3uf86nCp/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'HTM - prepare the requested data', ''),
(5107, '', '2025-04-25', 'BTA', '\nThis is to formally request a change in the location of the Multi-purpose Building Project originally programmed to be constructed at Lumbaca Unayan, Lanao Del Sur, under the Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) allocated to the undersigned for Fiscal Year (FY) 2022.\nDue to the death of the land donor and operational considerations, I believe that relocating the project would be beneficial.\nProject Name: Multi-purpose Building Project MP Ali B. Solaiman \nCurrent Location: Municipality of Lumbaca Unayan, Lanao Del Sur Requested \nNew Location: Municipality of Lumbatan, Lanao Del Sur', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1r2400rqk2GwMyYVMJkxibhgyeyfA2SwO/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'JMJ - verify project status; FAA', ''),
(5108, '', '2025-04-25', 'BTA', 'This is to formally request a change in the location of the CONSTRUCTION OF STREET LIGHTS originally programmed to be constructed at Brgy. Rorogagus, Marawi City, Lanao Del Sur, under the Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF) allocated to the undersigned for Fiscal Year (FY) 2024. I believe that relocating the project would be beneficial to our fellow Bangsamoro.\nThe purpose of the said change of location is due to duplication or overlapping of projects.\nProject Name: Construction of Street Light, MP Ali B. Solaiman TDIF FY 2024\nCurrent Location: Brgy. Rorogagus, Marawi City, Lanao Del Sur\nRequested New Location: Purok Cadayon Ragayan Boundary, Brgy. Cadayunan II, Marawi City, Lanao Del Sur', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1srV49jqoCmAqx3ooYzbnRudfhdY4OjWL/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'JMJ - kindly assess', ''),
(5109, '', '2025-04-25', 'BTA', '\nWe are writing to inform your esteemed Ministry of a change in the address of the project under the Transitional Development Impact Fund concerning the concreting of a barangay road.\nThe original location of the proposed project of $24-SF21CC231 - Concreting of Barangay Road/FMR along MaÃ±ara and Jarabelo Street, Happy Homes Subdivision, Rosary Heights 10, Cotabato City\" has been relocated. The new project site is now along Izrael Pinguiaman Street, Purok Awal, T.V. Jualiano Avenue. This change was necessary due to an overlap with an existing road project under the MPW Regular Infrastructure Projects. MP HASHEMI M. DILANGALEN', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1dOWlEQOjSW31MTKBWkjadde8HxoxNxkA/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'KNM - verify project status. print the summary of SF project w/ concerns.', ''),
