(5113, '', '2025-04-29', 'MDS', '\nSubmission of 2 Sets of Survey Report\nSubmitting the Survey Report Under the General Appropriation Act for the Bangsamoro 2025 (GAAB 2025)\nListed below.\nConstruction of Road at Sitio Namli - Sitio Mimbago, Brgy. Layog. Pagalungan, Maguindanao del sur\nConcreting of Road at Sitio Binaton-Sitio Duka - Sitio Lumbos, Brgy. Romongaob (Phase 2), South Upi, Maguindanao del sur', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1z99AsLzwx5cHs1KhTWfTNttqv0bGLih-/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'KNM - coordinate w/ prev. validating team. how was this not known. was there no LGU rep. during validation; check validation certification.', ''),
