(5116, '', '2025-04-30', 'MAFAR', 'We would like to inform you that the Bangsamoro Project Advisory Board (BPAB) of the Mindanao Inclusive Agriculture Development Project (MIADP) will hold a meeting on May 2, 2025 in MAFAR Conference, Cotabato City. The purpose of the meeting is to conduct orientation and deliberation on the MIADP AD-ENTREP proposed subproject \"Consolidation and Marketing of Marine Products (Big eye scad, Crabs, Red Snapper, and Grouper) for the Sama Bangingi community (CADT No. R09-LAN0206-043) in Hadji Muhtamad.', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1RfioBDErZDx-R_zeIcuEo4BxjBfXbDEB/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'MSA - kindly attend secure min. of meeting', ''),
(5117, '', '2025-04-30', 'MDN', 'We are submitting herewith the Plans and Programs of Works of the Project stated below to be implemented By Contract under FY 2024 Transitional Development Impact Fund (TDIF), to wit:Maguindanao del Norte:Construction of Tire Path (Phase 2),Sitio Tapukan, Brgy. Pigcalagan, Sultan Kudarat', '', '', '', '', 'PLANNING SECTION', 'https://drive.google.com/file/d/1Y9gyQ91OPwnGcFSaQb41ZbwCRyPi8Sqe/view?usp=sharing', '', '', 'NGC - FAA', ''),
